  "stem": "<p>Line&nbsp;<math alttext=\"script l\"><mi mathvariant=\"script\">l</mi></math> is defined by <math alttext=\"3 y plus 12 x equals 5\"><mn>3</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>. Line <math alttext=\"n\"><mi>n</mi>\n</math> is perpendicular to line&nbsp;<math alttext=\"script l\"><mi mathvariant=\"script\">l</mi></math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane. What is the slope of line <math alttext=\"n\"><mi>n</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
